## 1. Project Overview

### System Topology
```
3S Li-ion 18650 ×3 (9V–12.6V, 11.1V nom)
        │
        [F1: 15A Blade Fuse]
        │
        [Q1: IRF9540N TO-220 P-MOSFET — Reverse Polarity Protection]
        │
        ├──→ J2.P1 (VBAT_SWITCHED) → [XL4016-A external] → 6V/10A → J2.P2/P3 (+6V_SERVO)
        │                                                             → J6.P5 → PCA9685 V+
        ├──→ J3.P1 (+5V) ← [XL4016-B external] → 5V/10A
        │         → U1 (AMS1117-3.3) → +3V3
        │         → J10.P1 → RPi 5V
        │         → J13.P15 → ESP32 VIN
        └──→ J9 (L298N control signals ONLY — no power through J9)
```

### Power Rails

| Rail | Source | Max Current | Consumers |
|------|--------|-------------|-----------|
| +VBAT | 3S Li-ion | 15A (fused) | Q1 input |
| /VBAT_SWITCHED | Q1 output | 15A | J2.P1 → XL4016-A input |
| +6V_SERVO | XL4016-A external | 10A | J2.P2/P3 → J6.P5 → PCA9685 V+ → MG996R servos |
| +5V | XL4016-B external | 10A | RPi 5, ESP32 VIN, U1 input |
| +3V3 | AMS1117-3.3 on PCB | 1A | ESP32 VCC, IMU, I2C pull-ups |
| GND | Solid plane In1.Cu | — | All returns |

