## 3. Bill of Materials — AS PLACED

### 3.1 Power Input & Protection

| Ref | Qty | Component | Value | Package | Nets | Notes |
|-----|-----|-----------|-------|---------|------|-------|
| J1 | 1 | 2-pin header | VBAT_IN | 2-pin 2.54mm | +VBAT, GND | ⚠ 2.54mm header rated ~3A — undersized for 15A. Replace with XT-60 or 5.08mm screw terminal before use |
| F1 | 1 | Fuse holder | 15A blade | 2-pin 2.54mm | +VBAT, Net-(Q1-S) | ⚠ PCB footprint is pin header — must use proper blade fuse holder in harness |
| Q1 | 1 | P-MOSFET | IRF9540N | TO-220-3_Vertical | Net-(Q1-G), /VBAT_SWITCHED, Net-(Q1-S) | Reverse polarity protection |
| D1 | 1 | TVS Diode | SMBJ12A | D_SMB | GND, /VBAT_SWITCHED | Transient suppression — clamp at 12V |
| R5 | 1 | Resistor | 10kΩ | Axial THT | +VBAT, Net-(Q1-G) | Gate divider upper |
| R6 | 1 | Resistor | 10kΩ | Axial THT | Net-(Q1-G), GND | Gate divider lower |

**Gate Divider — IRF9540N:**
```
VBAT → [R5: 10kΩ] → Gate ← [R6: 10kΩ] ← GND
Vgs = -(VBAT × 0.5)
At 12.6V: Vgs = −6.3V   IRF9540N threshold: −2V to −4V → FET ON ✓
```

